  <h2>Biography</h2>
  <p>Bill Saxelby is a proven leader who has a track record of creating shareholder value with diverse experiences in product manufacturing, distribution and services businesses.</p>
  <p>He has been both a CEO and Board member in public and private companies for 13 years with a strong background in strategy and market development.</p>
  <p>He has worked primarily in the healthcare industry and also has experience in industrial businesses, food service and agriculture.</p>
  <p>Bill’s primary objective is to seek a CEO, President or senior operating position where his 42 years of experience can add value to an organization that would benefit from his market and customer-centric, team-first approach to managing.</p>
